get in my way, son.

479
00:26:30,156 --> 00:26:31,758
If I have to
go through you,

480
00:26:31,791 --> 00:26:34,260
I'm gonna leave
one hellacious hole.

481
00:26:34,293 --> 00:26:35,862
Hey, hey, hey,
hey, Pop.

482
00:26:35,895 --> 00:26:37,363
You be careful
how you talk to him.

483
00:26:37,396 --> 00:26:38,765
We could be
a family soon.

484
00:26:38,798 --> 00:26:40,900
Family? I--
I'm your family.

485
00:26:40,933 --> 00:26:42,635
Okay.
Fine, then.

486
00:26:42,669 --> 00:26:45,171
You can do the dishes.
We're gonna go to bed.

487
00:26:45,204 --> 00:26:46,806
You want me
